name: .1TE File Extension
summary: Learn about .1TE files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: To use a 1TE file with 1tracker (Windows, Linux):
Place the file in 1tracker's engines directory.
Open 1tracker and press F7 to access the Select engine menu.
Scroll to the engine your 1TE file contains.
Press CTRL + ENTER to select your engine and apply the settings it contains.
